\begin_inset Formula $n_{\text{v}}=\rho\sum_{\alpha}q_{\alpha}g_{\alpha}$
\end_inset

, appearing in the expression for the solvent electrostatic potential 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{\text{v}}$
\end_inset

