 The corresponding two values for the free energy, 
\begin_inset Formula $G_{\text{MM}}=E[n_{\text{u}}^{(0)}]+\mu[\bar{n}_{\text{u}}^{(0)}]$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $G_{\text{PT1}}=E[n_{\text{u}}^{(0)}]+\mu[n_{\text{u}}^{(0)}]$
\end_inset

